President Muhammadu Buhari has expressed "deeply sadness" over the air crash that claimed the lives of the Chief of Army Staff, Lt. Gen. Ibrahim Attahiru, and other military officers. Attahiru and 11 others, including four crew members had died in a plane crash close to Kaduna on Friday. President Buhari receives briefing on the Plane crash which led to the death of the Chief of Army Staff Lt. Gen. Ibrahim Attahiru and others in State House on 21st May 2021
